Method Detail

search

public Cursor search(QueryFilter f)
Returns Data in the form of a Cursor from a Searchable object. The given QueryFilter is passed to the search method, and the Searchable object returns a Cursor that contains the resulting search Data.

Parameters:
f - the Query that defines the search
Returns:
the corresponding Cursor
